1. SKYAI pre-sale has raised about $50 million, and will hold an AMA at 8 pm today;
2. The Vietnamese Ministry of Finance cooperated with Bybit to launch a pilot project for crypto trading and establish a legal framework;
3. US spot ETP purchased more than 529,000 bitcoins, far exceeding the number of mining outputs in the same period;
4. Abraxas Capital-related wallets have withdrawn nearly $250 million in bitcoins in the past four days;
5. Galaxy Digital withdrew 606,000 SOLs from the exchange in the past four days and pledged 462,000 SOLs;
6. ANAP, a Tokyo Stock Exchange-listed company, announced that it has purchased 16.6591 BTC;
7. A diamond hand was hit hard by the LUCE crash, from a profit of $5.2 million to a loss of $335,000;
8. A whale transferred 7,488 ETH, worth about $11.92 million, and the wallet still holds 10,322 ETH;
9. Analysis: After the "tariff storm", the year-end forecast for Bitcoin was lowered to $85,000;
10. The author of "Rich Dad Poor Dad" reiterated the impending financial disaster and recommended buying gold, silver and Bitcoin;
11. Analyst: The group that holds the currency for 3-6 months recently transferred about 170,000 BTC, which may cause price fluctuations.
